com.smjourney.map

Class Map<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.smjourney.map.Map<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the element that each separate Cell on the Map stores.

    public class Map<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    A Map that stores all elements situated on each seperate Cell of it and each of their individual data.
